title: Getting To Know Your Inner Bitch
itunes:title: Getting To Know Your Inner Bitch
description:
Your inner bitch is the voice inside your head. She's cranky, demanding, and often has the same tone as yo' mamma.
 
If you've ever wished she'd just go away or wondered why she talks so ugly to you, then this is YOUR podcast.
 
You'll learn how to deal with her and if it's possible to stop her.
 
Get the Free Course here:
http://phit.click/freecourse
